  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Phobos Down</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Phobos Down is a twin stick shooter stripped down to the bare essentials with focus on smooth controls and satisfying action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754880/extras/353690ec29851da072255fb57196c77a.poster.avif?t=1765178321\" width=552 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754880/extras/353690ec29851da072255fb57196c77a.webm?t=1765178321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754880/extras/353690ec29851da072255fb57196c77a.mp4?t=1765178321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You're a lone corporation contract worker sent to salvage lost cargo on a distant uncharted planet full of hostile lifeforms. Mow down waves of unique enemies earning access to better equipment and customize your weapons to suit your play style.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a player with three guns, swarms of enemies that need killing and a weapon upgrade system made as simple as possible. You can play unique randomized missions or weekly challenges where everyone play the same game and compete for the highest scores.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated missions. Every run is different</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slower-paced strategic shooter action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play one mission at a time. Pause at any point. No time limits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weekly challenges with online high scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed specifically with Steam Deck in mind</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Phobos Down</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Phobos Down is a twin stick shooter stripped down to the bare essentials with focus on smooth controls and satisfying action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754880/extras/353690ec29851da072255fb57196c77a.poster.avif?t=1765178321\" width=552 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754880/extras/353690ec29851da072255fb57196c77a.webm?t=1765178321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754880/extras/353690ec29851da072255fb57196c77a.mp4?t=1765178321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You're a lone corporation contract worker sent to salvage lost cargo on a distant uncharted planet full of hostile lifeforms. Mow down waves of unique enemies earning access to better equipment and customize your weapons to suit your play style.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a player with three guns, swarms of enemies that need killing and a weapon upgrade system made as simple as possible. You can play unique randomized missions or weekly challenges where everyone play the same game and compete for the highest scores.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated missions. Every run is different</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slower-paced strategic shooter action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play one mission at a time. Pause at any point. No time limits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weekly challenges with online high scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed specifically with Steam Deck in mind</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
